# Negative fixture: wtest_map_test runs bin/wtest_map_check on this file
# with expect_fail — it guards the checker itself. A checker that stopped
# failing would silently pass every selection regression, so this pins
# the failure path end-to-end: docs/todo.txt selects nothing, therefore
# the expect below must produce a 'wtest_map_check: FAIL' and exit 1.
# The real expectations live in tests/wtest/map_expectations.expect.
case docs/todo.txt
expect win64_hello_test
